Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."OPEN_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT"))

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" < 10 THEN '< 10 Days' WHEN "%1" < 20 THEN 'Between 10 and 20 Days' WHEN "%1" < 50 THEN 'Between 20 and 50 Days' WHEN "%1" > 50 THEN '> 50 Days' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Lead Age" < 10 THEN '< 10 Days' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Lead Age" < 20 THEN 'Between 10 and 20 Days' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Lead Age" < 50 THEN 'Between 20 and 50 Days' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Lead Age" > 50 THEN '> 50 Days' END

LogicalColumn.Description: Days in Stage Category

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE "%1" WHEN 'N' THEN CASE WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "%2", VALUEOF("%3")) < 31 THEN '0-30' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "%2", VALUEOF("%3")) < 61 THEN '31-60' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "%2", VALUEOF("%3")) < 91 THEN '61-90' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "%2", VALUEOF("%3")) > 90 THEN '91+' END END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."CLOSED_FLG" WHEN 'N' THEN CASE WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."STG_START_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT")) < 31 THEN '0-30' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."STG_START_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT")) < 61 THEN '31-60' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."STG_START_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT")) < 91 THEN '61-90' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."STG_START_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT")) > 90 THEN '91+' END END

LogicalColumn.name: # Days in Stage
LogicalColumn.Description: Average # of days that an opportunity spends in a sales-cycle stage

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE "%1" WHEN 'N' THEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "%2", VALUEOF("%3")) END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."CLOSED_FLG" WHEN 'N' THEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."STG_START_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT")) END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" > "%2" THEN 'Stalled' WHEN "%1" <= "%2" THEN 'Active' ELSE NULL END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."# Days in Stage" > "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Maximum Days In Sales Stage" THEN 'Stalled' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."# Days in Stage" <= "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Maximum Days In Sales Stage" THEN 'Active' ELSE NULL END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 'Y' THEN 0 WHEN "%2" > VALUEOF("%3") THEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , VALUEOF("%3"), "%2") END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."CLOSED_FLG" = 'Y' THEN 0 WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."CLOSE_DT" > VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT") THEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT"), "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_OPTY_D"."CLOSE_DT") END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL OR "%1" <= 7 THEN 'A: 0-7' WHEN "%1" <= 14 THEN 'B: 8-14' WHEN "%1" <= 21 THEN 'C: 15-21' WHEN "%1" <= 28 THEN 'D: 22-28' ELSE 'E: 29+' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Days Past Close Date" IS NULL OR "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Days Past Close Date" <= 7 THEN 'A: 0-7' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Days Past Close Date" <= 14 THEN 'B: 8-14' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Days Past Close Date" <= 21 THEN 'C: 15-21' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Opportunity"."Days Past Close Date" <= 28 THEN 'D: 22-28' ELSE 'E: 29+' END

Expr.name: Expr
